name: Fast Food (itch) (Saahil Talha)
description:
Fast Food - An infinite fast-paced game. It's fast food after all. It's all about eating food. Nothing else.

--Instructions--

=> Eat all the food - don't miss any unless they look bad/moldy.

=> You can make 3 mistakes, but no more, or else the game ends.

=> There are 7 unlockable characters, can you get them all?

=> You can select any of the two controls in-game.

--Credits--
